   version stable 0.15
  category audio/editor
 attribute console
    source http://lly.org/~rcw/id3/id3_$VERSION.orig.tar.gz
      info good 20120609
      info last 20090801
      info home http://lly.org/~rcw/id3/
 freshmeat none
      desc 'mp3 tag editing program
id3 is a music stream tagging program
that follows the ID3 specification.
It stores the following info in a tag:
* 30 character Artist name
* 30 character Album name
* 30 character Title name
*  4 character Year
* 30 character comment
*   enumerated Genre'


build(){
 sed -i "s:-g -O2:$CFLAGS:" Makefile
 make &&
 make install DESTDIR=$DESTDIR
}
